{"tid":433227,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【風暴消息】周日又打風？ 熱帶氣旋料闖港450公里","createTime":"2017-10-12T08:10:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-12T08:26:38.000Z","uid":78732,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"abcba5c588a5347da49c1d550162aa170f3eae4f","tid":433227,"uid":78732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T08:10:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57321641&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20171012\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57321641%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20171012&d=zxSEwzIAsp08fc7Qcb1rKWowyooGr0BEXXUM5gBrg7E%3D&h=92c0fcc2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57321641%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20171012&h=5257912e\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57321641&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20171012</a><br />\n<br />\n【12:00 更新】在正午12時，位於菲律賓以東的熱帶低氣壓集結在馬尼拉之東北約580公里，預料向西移動，時速約22公里，移向呂宋並逐漸增強。<br />\n<br />\n周日又打風？天文台指出，現時位於菲律賓以東的低壓區已增強為熱帶低氣壓，料會在今晚或明早命名為「卡努」(Khanun，泰國提供，為波羅蜜果，亦即大樹菠蘿)。<br />\n<br />\n以天文台現時的預測路徑，預料「卡努」會在明日晚上殺入本港800公里，一路向西進發，在下周日有機會增強至接近颱風級別，距離香港約450公里。<br />\n<br />\n由於預料本港會受東北季候風與該熱帶氣旋的共同影響，風勢頗大及有雨，如沒有掛波，將極大機會發出強烈季候風信號，即掛黑球，離岸風勢相當3號風球風力，海上或有大浪或暗湧，因此大家周日往海上活動要小心。<br />\n<br />\n氣溫方面，天文台亦預料下周日最低氣溫會跌至23&deg;C，較今日最高的32&deg;C跌約9&deg;C。大家往吹風時記緊添衣以防着涼。"},{"pid":"10ad8cc223fdec06902b6bef4040c00ec78a5c15","tid":433227,"uid":144113,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T08:12:39.000Z","msg":"舞雷公咁遠，仲要400公里都入唔到，就話打風<br />\n蘋果你收一收皮好冇？"},{"pid":"04523e236989eca7230aefe9833abea76e4aad84","tid":433227,"uid":55851,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T08:14:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>舞雷公咁遠，仲要400公里都入唔到，就話打風<br />\n蘋果你收一收皮好冇？</blockquote><br />\n個風未嚟已經比蘋果燈走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67cb53bc780899f64b35db980c146e7e4cf89111","tid":433227,"uid":102096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T08:15:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a3147400e95a4ff570a864e715c9b43b55dfc734","tid":433227,"uid":68746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T08:26:06.000Z","msg":"星期一先來<br />\n正仆街"},{"pid":"3dbdd8de5f0bec7012c4662fbb4cd6faede2f5ab","tid":433227,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T08:26:38.000Z","msg":"落大雨正仆街"}]}